---
layout: base.njk
title: "Signal — Join the waitlist"
description: "Get early access to Signal — a professional fit-scoring agent trained on your actual AI work history."
pageScript: /assets/js/waitlist.js
---

<div class="waitlist-page">
  <div class="waitlist-content-wrap">
  <div class="waitlist-page-inner">

    <h1 class="waitlist-headline">You've done the work.<br>Now let it speak.</h1>

    <div class="waitlist-body">

      <div>
        <div class="signal-qualify-block">
          <div id="waitlist-default">
            <p class="signal-qualify-heading">Signal is expanding to support:</p>
            <ul class="signal-qualify-list">
              <li>Designers, writers, and researchers using AI tools</li>
              <li>Active job seekers ready to make a move</li>
              <li>People still moving towards daily use</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin: 0 0 1rem;">If this is you, please leave your email so I can reach out personally when Signal is ready to support you.</p>
            <form id="waitlist-form" class="signal-waitlist-form">
              <input
                type="email"
                id="waitlist-email"
                class="signal-waitlist-input"
                placeholder="your@email.com"
                required
                autocomplete="email"
              />
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="waitlist-submit">Join waitlist</button>
            </form>
            <p id="waitlist-error" class="signal-waitlist-error" style="display:none"></p>
          </div>

          <div id="waitlist-success" style="display:none">
            <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 1rem;">Check your inbox.</h2>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">We sent a message to <strong id="waitlist-confirm-email" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);"></strong>. Please check your email to confirm your waitlist spot. If it's not there, check spam.</p>
          </div>

          <div id="waitlist-confirmed" style="display:none">
            <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 1rem;">Email confirmed.</h2>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">You're on the list. Thanks for being here early.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="signal-waitlist-demo-link">Not sure yet? <a href="/demo/">See a live demo →</a></p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <blockquote class="signal-pull-quote">
          <p>&#8220;I built Signal because I was tired of polishing a version of myself instead of doing the work I love. Great work should speak for itself. Let&#8217;s create a better way to get discovered.&#8221;</p>
          <cite class="signal-pull-quote-cite">&mdash; <a href="https://erikburns.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Erik Burns</a>, creator of Signal</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  <img src="/assets/images/signal_monkey_bg.png" alt="" class="waitlist-bg-img" aria-hidden="true">
</div>
